<br>
Memorable moments:<br>
<br>
When we first went thru the warpgate at forseral and headed to our target base, an enemy reaver snuck up behind us and killed Kirver almost instantly. The rest of us turned around and swarmed him. I think he had a heart attack. He &quot;tried&quot; to run. Tried.<br>
<br>
Later on in a fierce battle with the VS over a few bases, we came across an entire NC column of vanguards, lightnings, sunderers, enforcers, harrasers. In our first pass we wasted 2 vanguards as they had all bumped into each other making easy reaver targets. We got the sunderer and a lightning next, then it got all chaotic. There were friendlies fighting them at the same time on the ground but I think they musta dumped a load when we first arrived on the scene.<br>
<br>
<br>
I think we'll have to do that again when we have 10+. And we can practice staying together and in formation.<br>
<br>
Good job guys! It was great fun!<br>
